Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.62,0:03:03.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是星黄泉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.65,0:03:05.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上给我滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.89,0:03:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太轻松了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:14.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖忍法  影分身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.47,0:03:17.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇姑娘…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.03,0:03:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说\N那个家谱上写的戈薇是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.57,0:03:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.48,0:03:28.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北条  你快点拿着乾之刃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:29.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去风雷神社
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.35,0:03:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怎么可以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:38.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不会丢下\N戈薇姑娘一个人离开的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.36,0:03:47.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.47,0:03:53.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.07,0:03:57.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你释放出来的力量\N全部都被这把刀吸收了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.11,0:04:03.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.46,0:04:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.29,0:04:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这股妖气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.46,0:04:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是星黄泉的\N坤之刃散发出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.07,0:04:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们没事吧  戈薇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.71,0:04:35.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇姑娘  戈薇姑娘她…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.28,0:04:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:43.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.79,0:04:45.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  接下来要怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.36,0:04:50.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算赔上这个女人的性命\N也想要保护那把乾之刃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.16,0:04:53.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.80,0:05:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第139话 升云瀑步之大决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.38,0:05:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.58,0:05:09.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.32,0:05:15.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭那把生锈的刀\N能砍得了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.69,0:05:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁碎牙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:26.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要救这个女人的话\N就来风雷神社吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.96,0:05:31.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然\N不要忘了把乾之刃也带来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.70,0:05:32.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.34,0:05:40.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.04,0:05:42.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.91,0:05:44.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下也要一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:45.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只会碍事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.55,0:05:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请带我一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.92,0:05:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个都先等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.72,0:05:52.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得枫婆婆曾经说过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.99,0:05:56.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风雷神社应该是一个\N能够封印乾坤薙刀的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.93,0:05:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么他还要选择那个地方\N作为交换地点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.56,0:06:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定这是个陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没有时间考虑这么多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我的不幸\N害得戈薇姑娘也被卷入
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.74,0:06:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.08,0:06:15.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一块去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.01,0:06:16.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,云母
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.88,0:06:19.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.60,0:06:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在要开始进行\N乾坤薙刀的复活仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.77,0:06:47.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让那帮家伙接近神社
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.54,0:06:49.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:06:59.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个半妖就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.12,0:07:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭他那生锈的刀\N不是我的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.42,0:07:03.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  法师就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.56,0:07:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来对付那个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.56,0:07:10.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么\N我就选那个年轻的武士咯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:32.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.22,0:07:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么光
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.90,0:07:42.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.25,0:07:58.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此路不通哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你闻起来好像很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.19,0:08:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是月之青龙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.49,0:08:08.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来交个朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.20,0:08:15.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚  你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.00,0:08:17.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的对手是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:25.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝  你振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.37,0:08:26.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒一醒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.58,0:08:29.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此只好这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.21,0:08:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.02,0:08:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你醒过来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.46,0:08:44.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好像一下子全都走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:46.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们快点去找犬夜叉少爷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.40,0:08:47.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.06,0:08:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.00,0:08:53.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋时  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.60,0:08:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像闪到腰了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.24,0:08:57.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:08:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:01.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好迷人的小屁屁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:06.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是一位可爱的年轻武士耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.75,0:09:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是花之朱雀  请多指教哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:16.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰上我暗之玄武来当你的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:19.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的运气还真差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.73,0:09:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.60,0:09:24.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就凭你手上那把破刀\N还能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.27,0:09:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你聋了是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:28.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫你立刻滚开  听到了没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.81,0:09:32.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是有蚊子在叮我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.78,0:09:42.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.42,0:09:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对付你这种家伙\N还用不着铁碎牙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.83,0:09:52.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.33,0:09:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散魂铁爪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我说了没有用的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.21,0:10:05.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙的身体怎么那么硬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.34,0:10:06.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.84,0:10:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.68,0:10:12.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轮到我出招了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.95,0:10:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖忍法  龟甲地狱车
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你逃不掉的\N可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.83,0:10:30.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久没有\N找女人当猎物了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.03,0:10:32.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要好好享受一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.24,0:10:34.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  太恶心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.67,0:10:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞来骨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.98,0:10:41.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑…跑到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.59,0:10:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖忍法  鳞之舞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.37,0:11:04.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.50,0:11:09.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖忍法  逆鳞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.74,0:11:15.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚  我马上去救你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.88,0:11:20.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等打倒了我学之白虎再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.52,0:11:22.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得用风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.58,0:11:24.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想得逞  法师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.53,0:11:32.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  法师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.13,0:11:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.53,0:11:39.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放手\N我不会把乾之刃交给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.74,0:11:41.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不行喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.10,0:11:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖把乾之刃给我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.14,0:11:46.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就把你那张\N可爱的脸皮剥下来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.78,0:11:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摆在刀刃上当作装饰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不会让你得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.75,0:11:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  一点都不听话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:58.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么把你的脸做成壁饰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.62,0:12:00.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我每天早上都亲一下\N怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.66,0:12:04.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  太恶心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.56,0:12:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真看不下去  这世界全乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.13,0:12:10.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…再不振作的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.93,0:12:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狐火
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.77,0:12:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.20,0:12:15.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好烫  好烫  好烫…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.57,0:12:17.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想烫死我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.64,0:12:21.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢突然偷袭我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.58,0:12:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.95,0:12:35.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.96,0:12:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒过来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.83,0:12:47.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.84,0:12:49.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来好悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.34,0:12:53.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么  到底是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.68,0:12:58.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为人类的你\N为什么会和半妖一起旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:13:00.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和那半妖是什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.72,0:13:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要问这个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.58,0:13:04.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你一点关系都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.85,0:13:07.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类和妖怪之间\N是不能有爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到头来人类和妖怪\N终究不可能结合
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.33,0:13:14.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为人类\N总有一天会背叛妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.63,0:13:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天你也\N会背叛那个半妖的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.37,0:13:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.14,0:13:24.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类是一种很脆弱的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:25.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论身体  心灵都很脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.11,0:13:29.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明很脆弱\N却总是厚颜无耻的活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.51,0:13:33.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以人类\N会为了保全自己而背叛别人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.78,0:13:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想应该是你误会人类了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.52,0:13:39.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟人类发生过什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.65,0:13:42.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样的吧\N所以你才会说出这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女武士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.67,0:13:53.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那张画上的人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.80,0:13:56.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.38,0:14:07.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月黄泉\N你在这个地方干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.02,0:14:09.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.42,0:14:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.19,0:14:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,临  兵  斗  者  皆  阵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.29,0:14:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,列  在\N月黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.59,0:14:16.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.39,0:14:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.20,0:14:21.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你要这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.20,0:14:30.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.11,0:14:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.95,0:14:41.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样\N我在这里被月黄泉封印
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.95,0:14:44.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而乾坤薙刀中的乾之刃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.82,0:14:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞到了富士山那里的北条家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.29,0:14:50.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坤之刃则是被镇压在白灵山\N分隔两地收了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.23,0:14:54.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在白灵山崩塌之时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.86,0:14:58.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我取回了这把坤之刃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.24,0:15:05.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以枫婆婆才说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风雷神社\N是封印乾坤薙刀的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:12.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月黄泉背叛了我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.11,0:15:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还曾经说过\N要和我一起活在这世上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.98,0:15:17.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.32,0:15:19.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想月黄泉\N她一定有什么理由
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.62,0:15:22.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类是脆弱的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.76,0:15:24.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明很脆弱\N却为了想要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.49,0:15:26.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才会背叛别人苦恼不已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.13,0:15:31.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的愿望就是把人类\N从这种苦恼之中解救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.27,0:15:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算要怎么拯救人类
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.77,0:15:41.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唤醒这把用222只妖怪的骨骸\N打造出来的乾坤薙刀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.91,0:15:43.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再置人类于死地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.61,0:15:45.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样叫做解救人类吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:47.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这世上最无可救药的动物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:49.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以唯一能解救\N人类的方法就是死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.62,0:15:53.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:15:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不出我所料
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次看到你的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.16,0:16:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就感受到你散发出来的灵力强度\N和月黄泉是相同的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.80,0:16:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我为什么不在那里\N就把乾之刃夺走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.30,0:16:11.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还特地把你引到这里来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.31,0:16:12.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原因就是为了\N利用你所蕴藏的灵力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.91,0:16:16.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来进行乾坤薙刀的复活仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.81,0:16:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.32,0:16:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力量被…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.02,0:16:31.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么想要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.89,0:16:33.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.33,0:16:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被分开的乾之刃\N马上就会来到我的手中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.60,0:16:40.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.36,0:17:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.26,0:17:06.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋时爬上瀑步了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.10,0:17:13.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖忍法  龟甲碎击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:22.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你再也逃不了了  半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.85,0:17:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就安心的去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的尸体我会好好安葬的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:40.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒…法师…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.06,0:17:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.90,0:17:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在担心那个女人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.97,0:17:46.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:48.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上就会让你们\N在那个世界重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.04,0:17:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  接招
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.91,0:17:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虎口碎牙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.94,0:17:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.98,0:17:59.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我不知道\N你能够施展什么样的法力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.95,0:18:02.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你现在\N已经连动都动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.92,0:18:07.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝  你再不振作的话\N那该怎么办呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.39,0:18:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.42,0:18:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再不振作起来的话\N就什么都办不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.06,0:18:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋时  你再忍耐一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:18.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.63,0:18:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  抓住我  秋时
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.34,0:18:28.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让你跑掉的\N可爱的武士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.48,0:18:31.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.66,0:18:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彻底的压碎你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.09,0:18:44.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.50,0:18:48.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.14,0:18:55.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.98,0:19:02.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.21,0:19:04.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞刃血爪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.52,0:19:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.55,0:19:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.12,0:19:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚  快点找个东西抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.29,0:19:17.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.26,0:19:20.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:22.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.17,0:19:29.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.78,0:19:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟…糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.55,0:19:44.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.49,0:19:50.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.53,0:19:53.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.53,0:19:55.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.76,0:19:57.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.03,0:19:59.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.07,0:20:00.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还好…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.07,0:20:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们最好动作快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:04.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快去救戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.08,0:20:44.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧  秋时
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.28,0:20:46.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.65,0:20:50.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乾之刃飞到那神社里面去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.32,0:20:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事  这种不祥的感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.06,0:21:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.93,0:21:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在终于复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.83,0:21:06.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的乾坤薙刀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.93,0:21:08.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.64,0:21:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我来告诉你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.54,0:21:12.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乾坤就是阴和阳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.87,0:21:14.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是天和地的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.01,0:21:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森罗万象  所有位于\N相反两极的两股巨大力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.35,0:21:23.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用乾坤薙刀\N把这两股力量分开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.82,0:21:25.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将眼前所看不见的\N空间劈开的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.05,0:21:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道会怎么样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.06,0:21:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,废话少说  快把戈薇给放了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:32.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类是很脆弱的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.83,0:21:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类是会背叛的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.46,0:21:38.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我一定要把这片大地上\N所有的人类都消灭掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.22,0:21:56.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.12,0:21:58.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都被吸进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.45,0:22:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.06,0:22:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋时
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.47,0:22:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇姑娘在那里\N不能使用风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.67,0:22:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.14,0:22:22.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉\N铁碎牙的妖力还没有恢复吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.41,0:22:25.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.88,0:22:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.42,0:22:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一切…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.58,0:22:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一切都是我的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.92,0:22:33.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪我把戈薇姑娘\N卷入这么危险的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.75,0:22:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还落入那个家伙的手里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.92,0:22:38.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是说那些废话的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.69,0:22:39.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一定要想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.89,0:22:42.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把戈薇\N从那个怪物的手中救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.93,0:22:45.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.23,0:22:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁碎牙又还没有恢复…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.13,0:22:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管不了那么多了\N只要有决心总会有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.65,0:24:56.65,ED,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.95,0:23:19.65,ED,,0,0,0,,如今内心充满着悲伤的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.20,0:23:35.70,ED,,0,0,0,,尽管靠着我哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.67,0:23:41.77,ED,,0,0,0,,I get,I get,I get,get the feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.77,0:23:45.30,ED,,0,0,0,,I get,I get,I get,get the dreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.30,0:23:51.50,ED,,0,0,0,,就像现在这样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.77,0:24:01.77,ED,,0,0,0,,Come my way 这点黑暗之尘
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.77,0:24:09.72,ED,,0,0,0,,Come close to me 现在灯已照亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.72,0:24:12.82,ED,,0,0,0,,I'll be with you I'll be with you
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.25,0:24:17.50,ED,,0,0,0,,只是简简单单的陪在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.50,0:24:23.90,ED,,0,0,0,,So Come my way
